Package org.gbif.api.model.registry

Class MachineTag

java.lang.Object
org.gbif.api.model.registry.MachineTag
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, LenientEquals<MachineTag>
public class MachineTag extends Object implements LenientEquals<MachineTag>, Serializable
A tag that has a namespace, name and a value. created and createdBy are automatically set upon persisting.
